AIRS Platform — Alembic Migration Guide
========================================

Database: Aiven PostgreSQL 17.10 (pg-3434c-ai-hiring-platform1.l.aivencloud.com:14813)
Schema:   v2.1  |  31 tables  |  pgvector enabled

Common commands
---------------
Generate migration from model changes:
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"

Apply all pending migrations:
  alembic upgrade head

Rollback one migration:
  alembic downgrade -1

Show current revision:
  alembic current

Show migration history:
  alembic history --verbose

How it works
------------
env.py reads all DB_* variables from .env, imports all 12 model
modules so Base.metadata is populated, then diffs the DB against
the models to produce a migration script.

